text: Desmiphora lateralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1868. It is known from Brazil, Uruguay, and Paraguay.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora lateralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1868
